Day 7: Feedback Fuels Growth!
📈 "Feedback isn’t just a reflection—it’s a roadmap for improvement!"  
👉 Tip: Encourage constant feedback loops within the team. Growth comes from constructive conversations.

💡 𝗗𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘆 𝘁𝗶𝗽𝘀 for Scrum Teams and especially Scrum Masters! Get practical advice, best practices, & strategies to boost collaboration and sprint success.
